{"tid":1386114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［討論］市民主動控告警方？","createTime":"2019-07-30T09:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T01:40:14.000Z","uid":258521,"like":84,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"b281e85e93a98e62c30bb7e3a0970bfa76ac878d","tid":1386114,"uid":258521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:02:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知，一定有人話冇9用，5年前都試過唔work之類....<br />\n但我想提出嘅係，宜家個情況同5年前已經唔同了，宜家係眼盲嘅都睇到黑警嘅罪證，點解唔試多次呢？<br />\n<br />\n而宜家個正苦就擺明包庇警蓄，警蓄又包鄉黑，香港人宜家淨係得「以下克上」（街頭抗爭）。如果，開拓埋「以上克下」（國際刑事法庭），成個形勢就唔同曬，會更有利香港人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n------------------我係分隔線------------------<br />\n羅沃啟表示，如果市民曾經被警察毆打，或遭受過任何不人道的對待，都可以聯絡聯合國人權事務高級專員辦事處（Office of the United Nations High Commissioner for Human Rights，簡稱OHCHR）。他舉例指，<span style=\"color: gold;\">受害者可將驗傷報告、其他證據以及事發經過，以電郵或郵寄方式發送至OHCHR。雖然OHCHR未必有人手逐個個案去處理，但它會整體去進行調查及跟進。</span>他又指，市民亦可將資料交給香港人權監察，他會親身去跟進。<br />\n<br />\n至於「文化監暴」表示或會就警察濫權告上國際刑事法庭，羅沃啟則認為個別人士自己去做的難度相當高，<span style=\"color: gold;\">反而若聯合國有足夠資料時，可以代表香港人去國際刑事法庭訴訟；而且國際刑事法庭比較公平公正，不會顧慮中國的面子，「威力」不容忽視。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n汁：<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/70284/%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%8D%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%81%9A%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%EF%BC%9F%E2%94%80%E2%94%80%E6%B0%91%E4%BA%8B%E7%B4%A2%E5%84%9F%E3%80%81/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F70284%2F%25E9%259D%25A2%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B%25EF%25BC%258C%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%2581%259A%25E4%25BB%2580%25E9%25BA%25BC%25EF%25BC%259F%25E2%2594%2580%25E2%2594%2580%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25BA%258B%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%2584%259F%25E3%2580%2581%2F&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCuVtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=9d1f97fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/70284/%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%8D%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%81%9A%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%EF%BC%9F%E2%94%80%E2%94%80%E6%B0%91%E4%BA%8B%E7%B4%A2%E5%84%9F%E3%80%81/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7354b6b608d8f09a966c9f6d988817a4961e6837","tid":1386114,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:03:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85d1cdc4585603950ac14401914d943763a0c258","tid":1386114,"uid":157529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:04:00.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"7fa5624ba44d09645a908cef13c15660de7fc968","tid":1386114,"uid":192891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:04:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f56371dddf1f62ff1ef5df2d34605b7d9ce3d70","tid":1386114,"uid":283158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:04:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d0c1cb74df321be658edf8646d60cbfe2893613","tid":1386114,"uid":283741,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:05:45.000Z","msg":"除咗人權組織，仲要推埋上國際反恐組織，日日話黑警係恐怖分子，講得多自然有人招呼佢地"},{"pid":"28e905e289bfd79130c60c0086cbddbe12def751","tid":1386114,"uid":176102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:06:47.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"a5ff403198c0eae44da7505ce45dc80591ce9f6b","tid":1386114,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:07:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29f31297e15ee1eac814b9bb0cb85b5320111fe8","tid":1386114,"uid":276510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:08:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c17ad83e15f48277515815f6cf100c2324a645a3","tid":1386114,"uid":243366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:08:36.000Z","msg":"<img src